body:
I met the same issue.
```
FailedPreconditionError (see above for traceback): Failed to rename: ./logs/checkpoints/model_epoch-1.data-00000-of-00001.tempstate9288023132477748030 to: ./logs/checkpoints/model_epoch-1.data-00000-of-00001 : The process cannot access the file because it is being used by another process.
; Broken pipe
	 [[Node: save/SaveV2 = SaveV2[dtypes= ... ...
```
I did not sync this project with any online drive.

**I my case, It's `git` reading that file content.** So that file cannot be renamed. I added `logs/` to `.gitignore`, this error was fixed.
